Grab the butterknife.
Turn left. Pass the potato table and turn right. Go forward to the door, turn left. As you enter, turn left. Reach the wall and turn right. Approach the potato table. Turn left. Turn right.
Lower the potato.
Cut the potato vertically twice using the butterknife on the sidetable.
Take the potato.
Leave the room. Go straight ahead and when you reach the microwave, turn left. Move to the left. Reach the sink cabinet. Turn left.
Open the microwave. Place the potato on the left side. Close the microwave. Turn it on for three seconds. Open the microwave. Take out the potato. Close it.
Turn left. After passing the shelf, turn left. Reach the coffeetable, turn left.
Place the potato next to the coffeetable.
